* Azure Storage\nLifecycle Policies
** Purpose
***_ Complement Delta Lake retention
***_ Transition to cooler tiers
***_ Auto-delete old blobs
** Tiers
***_ Cool: accessible, higher access cost
***_ Archive: offline, requires restore
** Challenges with Delta
***_ File rewrite resets creation time
***_ Archived files fail queries
***_ OPTIMIZE/MERGE delay archival
** Strategies
***_ Partition data by date
***_ Set delta.timeUntilArchived property
***_ Create views to restrict access
***_ OPTIMIZE/VACUUM with predicates
@endmindmap
